docs.text: Hello, World to you all and more specifically, GitHub! Hello again. I am techmuse. You can call me tech or muse. I decided to make this GitHub site because all the cool kids do it seems these days. As you can see, I recently converted it to MarkDown to make it look nicer! If there is anything weird open an issue on the GitHub. This site is in very early stages so open a pull request to see what I could improve as time goes on and I plan to add more. Thank you for reading this and I will see you in the next one. Tech Bugs
